import pandas as pd
import numpy as np

df_log = pd.DataFrame({
    "run": ["R1"]*7 + ["R2"]*7 + ["R3"]*7,
    "day": list(range(1,8))*3,
    "glucose": [
        5.0,4.8,4.6,4.5,4.3,4.1,3.9,      # R1
        5.0,4.9,4.7,4.6,4.5,4.4,4.3,      # R2
        5.0,4.7,4.4,4.1,3.8,3.5,3.2       # R3 (Îπ†Î•∏ ÏÜåÎπÑ)
    ],
    "lactate": [
        0.8,0.9,1.0,1.1,1.2,1.3,1.4,
        0.8,0.85,0.9,0.95,1.0,1.05,1.1,
        0.8,1.0,1.3,1.6,1.9,2.2,2.5
    ]
})

df_baseline = pd.DataFrame({
    "run": ["R1","R2","R3"],
    "baseline_day": [2, 2, 2],
})
display(df_log, df_baseline)

# ÌíÄÏù¥

```python
df_merged = df_log.merge(df_baseline, how='left', on='run')
base = (df_merged.loc[df_merged['day']==(df_merged['baseline_day']), ['run','glucose']]
        .rename(columns={'glucose':'baseline_glucose'}))

df_merged = df_merged.merge(base, on='run', how='left')
display(df_merged)
df_merged['glucose_drop_rate'] = (df_merged['baseline_glucose']-df_merged['glucose'])/df_merged['baseline_glucose']
df_merged['rapid_drop'] = (df_merged['day']>=df_merged['baseline_day']) & (df_merged['glucose_drop_rate']>=0.3)
display(df_merged)
df_merged_sorted = df_merged.sort_values(by=['run','day'], ascending=[True, True])
run_feat = df_merged_sorted.groupby('run').agg(
    rapid_day_cnt = ('rapid_drop', 'sum'),
    first_rapid_day = ('rapid_drop', 'first'),
    lactate_last = ('lactate', 'last'),
).reset_index()
display(run_feat)
```

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np
fig, axes = plt.subplots(nrows=3, ncols=1, figsize=(7,6))
runs = ['R1', 'R2', 'R3']
for idx, run in enumerate(runs):
    axes[idx].plot(df_merged[df_merged['run']==run]['day'],df_merged[df_merged['run']==run]['glucose'])
    axes[idx].scatter(df_merged[(df_merged['run']==run) & (df_merged['rapid_drop'])]['day'],df_merged[(df_merged['run']==run) & (df_merged['rapid_drop'])]['glucose'], color='red')
    axes[idx].set_title(f'{run} Glucose Trend')
    axes[idx].set_xlabel('day')
    axes[idx].set_ylabel('glucose')
    axes[idx].axhline(df_merged[df_merged['run']==run]['baseline_glucose'].iloc[0], color = 'gray', linestyle='--')
    axes[idx].grid(False)
plt.show()
